---
const sectors = [
  { icon: 'solar:delivery-linear', label: 'Logistik & Distribusi' },
  { icon: 'solar:factory-linear', label: 'Manufaktur' },
  { icon: 'solar:shop-linear', label: 'Retail & FMCG' },
  { icon: 'solar:buildings-2-linear', label: 'Properti' },
  { icon: 'solar:case-round-minimalistic-linear', label: 'Jasa Profesional' },
  { icon: 'solar:health-linear', label: 'Kesehatan & Klinik' },
];
---
<section class="py-24 px-6 relative z-10" id="who-we-build-for">
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zinc-200 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 group">
    <div class="md:col-span-5 relative">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-zinc-400 uppercase mb-4">Target klien kami</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight leading-tight text-zinc-950 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:translate-x-2">
        Untuk Operasional, Keuangan, HR, dan Tim Lapangan
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-7 mt-1 md:mt-0 relative">
      <div class="absolute -left-6 top-0 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-200 to-transparent rounded-full transform scale-y-0 group-hover:scale-y-100 transition-transform duration-700 origin-top"></div>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 mb-6 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:text-zinc-700">
        Kami bekerja dengan bisnis Indonesia 50–500 karyawan di mana operasional internal sudah kompleks — dan sistem yang ada tidak lagi cukup untuk mendukung pertumbuhan.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-500 mb-10 transition-all duration-500 delay-100 group-hover:text-zinc-700">
        Kalau tim Anda masih mengandalkan proses yang hidup di spreadsheet, rantai email, atau tools yang hampir cocok tapi tidak benar-benar pas — di situlah kita mulai.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
        {sectors.map((s) => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-zinc-200/60 bg-zinc-50/50 hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-300 cursor-default group/tag">
            <iconify-icon icon={s.icon} class="text-lg text-zinc-400 group-hover/tag:text-zinc-700 transition-colors" style="stroke-width: 1.5;"></iconify-icon>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-600 group-hover/tag:text-zinc-900 transition-colors">{s.label}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
